These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
2 different games are played: scrabble, canasta
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, spy
The people have 2 different jobs:  firefighter, police-officer
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the police-officer##3
2. the person playing canasta is in an even position##4
3. the person watching spy movies is the person playing scrabble##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Game      | scrabble  | canasta   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | crime   |
| Job         | police-officer | firefighter |
| Transport     | jet-ski | taxi    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: avocado, cabbage
House: palace, cottage
2 different pets are kept: dog, rat
The people have 2 different jobs:  architect, videographer
1. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
2. the palace house is the videographer##1
3. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | avocado     | cabbage |
| House   | cottage | palace  |
| Pet           | rat         | dog     |
| Job     | architect   | videographer    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, entrepreneur
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: weightlifting, climbing
The people have 2 different hobbies: skydiving, rock-climbing
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Beverage    | soy-milk     | hot-chocolate |
| Job         | entrepreneur | accountant    |
| Sport         | weightlifting         | climbing        |
| Hobby   | skydiving         | rock-climbing    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, volleyball
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, action
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, cooking
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, pop
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
2. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
3. the fan of pop is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Sport      | volleyball     | ice-hockey |
| Movie-Genre          | action   | crime  |
| Hobby         | card-games | cooking     |
| Music-Genre   | classical  | pop         |

