.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-11::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, project-manager
City: berlin, miami
There are 2 different favourite colors: orange, apricot
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, basketball
1. the person who likes apricot is on the left or right of the person traveling to berlin##3
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
3. the project-manager is in an even position##4
4. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |        2        |
| Job           | accountant | project-manager |
| City   | berlin    | miami      |
| Color           | orange      | apricot          |
| Sport         | basketball | badminton       |

