.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-16::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: collecting, magic-tricks
The people have 2 different jobs:  firefighter, software-developer
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, december
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, hot-chocolate
1. the software-developer is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |      2      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks       | collecting  |
| Job           | software-developer | firefighter |
| Birthday   | december             | november      |
| Beverage   | tea              | hot-chocolate        |

