.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-20::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, water
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: orchid, dahlia
2 different pets are kept: frog, goat
2 different games are played: monopoly, canasta
1. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
3. the person playing monopoly is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate | water    |
| Flower         | dahlia        | orchid |
| Pet         | frog          | goat     |
| Game   | monopoly        | canasta     |

 